Remarks . This specimen agrees perfectly with the description of the neotype (
Álvarez-Campos et al. 2015b
), with small differences in size, number of articles of some cirri and other minor details. Distribution. Red Sea, Australia (Western Australia), English Channel; some previous dubious reports from the Mediterranean.
